# Belt-and-braces against agent-process files ever reaching a publish
# tarball. `.gitignore` keeps them from being tracked in the first
# place; `export-ignore` here strips them from `cargo publish` archives
# and `git archive` output even if one ever slipped past gitignore.
#
# Mirror the gitignored set in `.gitignore` and the AGENTS.md > "Where
# transient agent reports go" table.
.agent/             export-ignore
decisions/          export-ignore
proposals/          export-ignore
research/           export-ignore
bug-reports/        export-ignore
scripts/            export-ignore
services/           export-ignore
.pr-test/           export-ignore
heso-test-agent/    export-ignore
AGENT_FINDINGS*.md  export-ignore
REGRESSION_*.md     export-ignore
COMPATIBILITY.md    export-ignore
AUDIT_*.txt         export-ignore
pitch.html          export-ignore
pitch-assets/       export-ignore
